<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Health Care Awareness</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f9f9f9; }
        header { background: #2c3e50; color: white; padding: 20px 0; text-align: center; }
        nav ul { display: flex; justify-content: center; list-style: none; padding: 0; background: #34495e; margin: 0; }
        nav ul li { margin: 0 15px; }
        nav ul li a { color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 15px; display: block; }
        nav ul li a:hover { background: #2c3e50; }
        .container { padding: 20px; }
        section { margin-bottom: 40px; background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        h2 { color: #2c3e50; }
        footer { background: #2c3e50; color: white; text-align: center; padding: 10px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Health Care Awareness Programmes</h1>
    </header>
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#programmes">Programmes</a></li>
            <li><a href="#impact">Impact</a></li>
            <li><a href="#causes">Causes & Effects</a></li>
            <li><a href="#precautions">Precautions</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
    <div class="container">
        <section id="programmes">
            <h2>Awareness Programmes</h2>
            <p>Various healthcare awareness programmes are conducted globally to educate people on issues such as hygiene, nutrition, mental health, chronic diseases, and vaccination.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>National Health Mission (NHM)</li>
                <li>World Health Day Campaigns</li>
                <li>HIV/AIDS Awareness Drives</li>
                <li>Cancer Screening Camps</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="impact">
            <h2>Impact</h2>
            <p>These programmes have significantly improved public health by increasing awareness, early detection of diseases, and promoting healthy lifestyles. Key impacts include:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Improved hygiene practices</li>
                <li>Reduction in disease outbreaks</li>
                <li>Increased vaccination rates</li>
                <li>Better mental health support</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="causes">
            <h2>Causes & Effects</h2>
            <p>Unawareness about health often stems from lack of education, poor infrastructure, misinformation, and socioeconomic barriers. The effects include:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Spread of preventable diseases</li>
                <li>Late diagnosis and treatment</li>
                <li>High mortality and morbidity</li>
                <li>Economic burden on families and systems</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="precautions">
            <h2>Precautions</h2>
            <p>Preventive measures are crucial to ensure community health. Recommended precautions:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Maintain hygiene and sanitation</li>
                <li>Regular health check-ups</li>
                <li>Stay informed through credible sources</li>
                <li>Follow vaccination schedules</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </div>
